{
  "texts": [
    "Drawing upon an LLM specifically designed for standardizing locomotive maintenance data, this paper presents the development of an intelligent Q&A system for locomotive maintenance.",
    "The workflow of this system, which is based on the customized LLM, is illustrated in Fig. 16.",
    "First, the user inputs a question in natural language.",
    "The system then segments this question into individual words via Jieba, which facilitates the identification of named entities.",
    "These entities are subsequently scored via the customized LLM."
  ]
}